ces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時入黨"},{"pid":"f674cc1c9f8e4ad025a7ea45e3d0a7f45b38aae1","tid":2002790,"uid":328500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"新加坡為何想回歸中國"},{"pid":"38ebb2c7cd240350274cbaa2ea9f5230e1c88864","tid":2002790,"uid":321803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T13:21:15.000Z","msg":"啲罩假ga"},{"pid":"6b771942704da1b055e419a2102640c9257614be","tid":2002790,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"由美支雙邊合作(國防靠美國，經濟靠支那但同時懷疑支那)變左一面倒做埋支那應聲蟲，老豆(李光耀)見到個仔二世祖搞到咁樣，激到李光耀彈番起身"},{"pid":"cd248e6323a45d0ca50330efd91b0d252db28f5f","tid":2002790,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"國防靠美國，經濟靠支那互惠互利(雖然只係口號)合作同時懷疑支那<br />\n<br />\n支那坡以前既李光耀取代埋英屬香港個位(FF本黎香港獨立係要咁行呢套外交)黎做，結果不足5年就已經俾件二世祖敗曬"}]}